This Karamba theme was first designed by Robert Paskowitz, translated  and redesigned by Gai Shaked (costello) as a part of GNU/Linux Kinneret.

This theme displays the following information:

Time
Date
Current Weather (from weather.yahoo.com) *
4 day forecast (from weather.yahoo.com) *
Percent used CPU
Free RAM
Free space on Hard Drives (/home/knoppix and /mnt/hda1)
Traffic in/out on eth0

* - you may view the weather for any city in Israel that have a record on weather.yahoo.com.

Make sure you INSTALL the included font.
